sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Router as InferenceGraph Router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Transformer as Transformer Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Explainer as Explainer Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS

    Note over Client,Explainer: Flow 2: InferenceGraph Multi-Model Pipeline

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/graph:predict<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Router: Forward Request<br/>HTTP, mTLS (Service Mesh Identity)

    Router->>Transformer: Transform Input<br/>HTTP, mTLS (Service Mesh)
    Transformer->>Transformer: Preprocess Data
    Transformer-->>Router: Transformed Input

    Router->>Predictor: Predict<br/>HTTP, mTLS (Service Mesh)
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run Model Inference
    Predictor-->>Router: Prediction

    Router->>Explainer: Explain (Optional)<br/>HTTP, mTLS (Service Mesh)
    Explainer->>Explainer: Generate Explanation
    Explainer-->>Router: Explanation Result

    Router-->>Gateway: Final Response<br/>HTTP, mTLS
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
